## üìä Before vs After Comparison

| Aspect | Before | After |
|--------|--------|-------|
| **Hero Section** | Full-screen, content-limited | Content-focused, space-efficient |
| **Color Scheme** | Dark, traditional blues | Modern, accessible palette |
| **Navigation** | Basic, non-responsive | Modern, glass morphism |
| **Cards** | Heavy shadows, dated | Light, modern hover effects |
| **Typography** | Mixed fonts | Systematic Inter-based system |
| **Spacing** | Inconsistent | 4px base unit system |
| **Mobile** | Basic responsive | Mobile-first design |
| **Accessibility** | Limited | WCAG 2.1 AA compliant |
| **Performance** | Standard | Optimized animations |

