## üé® Design System Documentation

### **Color Palette**
```css
/* Primary Colors */
--primary-500: #3b82f6;    /* Main brand color */
--primary-600: #2563eb;    /* Interactive states */
--primary-700: #1d4ed8;    /* Hover/active */

/* Secondary Colors */
--secondary-500: #f59e0b;  /* Accent color */
--secondary-600: #d97706;  /* Darker accent */

/* Neutral Colors */
--gray-50: #f8fafc;        /* Backgrounds */
--gray-500: #64748b;       /* Text secondary */
--gray-900: #0f172a;       /* Text primary */
```

### **Typography Scale**
```css
/* Headings */
h1: 3rem (48px) - Hero titles
h2: 2.5rem (40px) - Page titles  
h3: 2rem (32px) - Section titles
h4: 1.5rem (24px) - Subsections

/* Body Text */
base: 1rem (16px) - Regular text
lg: 1.125rem (18px) - Large text
```

### **Spacing System**
```css
/* 4px Base Unit */
space-1: 0.25rem (4px)
space-2: 0.5rem (8px)
space-4: 1rem (16px)
space-6: 1.5rem (24px)
space-8: 2rem (32px)
```

